3. The Business Committee shall report to the House their recommendations—


(a) as to the remaining Proceedings in Committee on the said Bill, not later than the twenty-ninth day of January, nineteen hundred and sixty-two;

(b) as to the Proceedings on Consideration of the said Bill, and as to the allocation of time between those Proceedings and Proceedings on Third Reading, not later than the fifth day on which the House sits after the day on which the Proceedings in Committee are concluded.

6. The Business Committee shall report to the House their recommendations—


(a) as to the remaining Proceedings in Committee on the said Bill, not later than the twenty-ninth day of January, nineteen hundred and sixty-two;

(b) as to the Proceedings on Consideration of the said Bill, and as to the allocation of time between those Proceedings and Proceedings on Third Reading, not later than the fourth day on which the House sits after the day on which the Proceedings in Committee are concluded.
